    "Notwithstanding these challenges, the majority of pupils saw ChatGPT as having the capacity to eventually supplant conventional methods of seeking information.",
    "Wu and Yu (2023) investigated the impact of AI chatbots on students' learning results.",
    "The results indicated that AI chatbots had a substantial influence on the educational achievements of students.",
    "Moreover, AI chatbots exerted a more pronounced influence on students in tertiary education compared to those in primary and secondary education.",
